telnet @{"gopher.ncc.go.jp" rxs "ADDRESS term SEND 'open gopher.ncc.go.jp\r'"}

Look in the "Japan information" menu for documents related to Japanese
life and culture.
@endnode

@node t-ucmp1.berkeley.edu
telnet @{"ucmp1.berkeley.edu" rxs "ADDRESS term SEND 'open ucmp1.berkeley.edu\r'"}

The University of California at Berkeley's Museum of Palentology
runs several online exhibits. You can obtain GIF images of a variety of
