@endnode

@node t-wx.atmos.uiuc.edu
telnet @{"wx.atmos.uiuc.edu" rxs "ADDRESS term SEND 'open wx.atmos.uiuc.edu\r'"}

Look up weather forecasts for North America or bone up on your weather
facts.
